(404, 'Heads Up Note 2025-11-25T09:18:00.000+05:30: Hi team, Sharing the heads-up note for our investment in WorkAtoms which is a text to workflow builder for non-engineering knowledge work (e.g. content writing, social media monitoring, responding to inbound requests etc) - initial focus is on Marketing & GTM teams DeVC is investing $50K as part of a $2M SAFE round @ $10M post money valuation *Note: This is a founder-first investment (based on IIT-B signals) + Community Top Up to *[*Nikhil*](https://www.linkedin.com/in/nikhil-abraham)* from Cloud Chef (new DeVC Collective member in US). Hence, we have sized the cheque accordingly & will do more work in coming months as they tighten their GTM and sharpen their product (hopefully for a single vertical) * **Founders** 1. [Dhruv Jaglan](https://www.linkedin.com/in/dhruv-jaglan/) - CEO & Founder 1. IIT Bombay CS 2020 1. 2.5 YOE @ BabbleBots AI - was promoted from Founding Engineer to Co-Founder 1. 1.5 YOE @ LinkedIn India 1. From Cash:* ++ soft refs from IIT-B network on Dhruv : “Rockstar and would get anything done”, “Machau ladka hai.. keeps picking new things and building”* 1. [Georgi Boby](https://www.linkedin.com/in/georgi-boby-07b081161/) - COO & Co-Founder 1. 6.5 YOR @ Cloudchef as Founding Engineer 1. IIT Bombay 2019 1. From Cash: *++ Table thumping ref on Georgi from Nikhil @ Cloud Chef and Ashray @ Rephrase AI* **Investing Process** 1. We were introduced to Dhruv Jaglan (main founder) via Activate AI (Aakrit & Pratyush) 1. Act...'),
